{"chapter_number":112,"name_simple":"Al-Ikhlas","verses_count":4,"verses":[{"text_madani":"قُلْ هُوَ اللَّهُ أَحَدٌ","translation_en":"Say: He, Allah, is One.","translation_id":"Katakanlah (Muhammad), “Dialah Allah, Yang Maha Esa."},{"text_madani":"اللَّهُ الصَّمَدُ","translation_en":"Allah is He on Whom all depend.","translation_id":"Allah tempat meminta segala sesuatu."},{"text_madani":"لَمْ يَلِدْ وَلَمْ يُولَدْ","translation_en":"He begets not, nor is He begotten.","translation_id":"(Allah) tidak beranak dan tidak pula diperanakkan."},{"text_madani":"وَلَمْ يَكُن لَّهُ كُفُوًا أَحَدٌ","translation_en":"And none is like Him.","translation_id":"Dan tidak ada sesuatu yang setara dengan Dia.”"}]}
